WEBVTT

00:13:28.841 --> 00:13:33.474
I did everything I could
to accommodate this person --

00:13:33.498 --> 00:13:36.950
this person did a perfectly OK job --

00:13:36.974 --> 00:13:40.236
we were extremely glad
when it was all over.

00:13:40.673 --> 00:13:46.275
And I heard later

00:13:46.299 --> 00:13:50.728
that she had commented
on the experience of "3rd Rock"

00:13:50.752 --> 00:13:54.116
and had said about me,
"Well, he's awfully needy."

00:13:54.482 --> 00:13:56.823
She was used to tyrannizing everybody.

00:13:57.307 --> 00:13:59.918
And my response to that was,

00:13:59.942 --> 00:14:03.712
"Let's at least make this
a bearable experience